# Voynich Manuscript: Complete Four-Layer Interlinear Translation

**All 201 Folios with EVA, Croatian Shorthand, Expanded Croatian, and English**

## Reading Guide

Each line shows four layers:
- **EVA:** Original EVA transcription
- **CRO:** Croatian shorthand (direct conversion using ZFD key)
- **EXP:** Expanded Croatian (shorthand expanded to full words)
- **ENG:** English translation (where vocabulary is known, ? = unknown)

## The ZFD Three-Layer Key

| Layer | Position | Mapping |
|-------|----------|---------|
| Operators | Word-initial | q/qo -> ko, ch -> h, sh -> š |
| Gallows | Medial | k -> st, t -> tr, f -> pr, p -> pl |
| Suffixes | Word-final | y -> i, n -> n, r -> r, m -> m |

## Key Vocabulary

| Croatian | Expanded | English |
|----------|----------|---------|
| kost | kost | bone |
| ol | ulje | oil |
| ar | voda/aqua | water |
| dar | dar | dose/gift |
| hedi | kuhati | cooked |
| šedi | močiti | soaked |
| kor | korijen | root |
| trav | trava | herb |
| sal | sol | salt |
